OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FSet over the course of a single,
OL,8,Fsurreal night, Sufiyaan's winning
OL,9,Fsubmission, Wimmy Road Boyz, follows
OL,10,Fthree men in their early twenties who
OL,11,Fdrive up and down Manchester's Curry
OL,12,FMile, bringing all of their baggage
OL,13,Fwith them.
OL,15,FIn pursuit of a wild time, these boys
OL,16,Fdon't yet know that their first night
OL,17,Fout in so long will also be their last.
OL,19,FThe 26-year-old's debut novel explores
OL,20,Fheartbreak, masculinity, friendship,
OL,21,Ffaith and class.
