OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FSufiyaan said: "It's still sinking in,
OL,8,Fbut wow - I'm beyond excited to be
OL,9,Fgiven the opportunity to have my work
OL,10,Fpublished with Penguin.
OL,12,F"Having met the talented writers on
OL,13,Fthe shortlist, I know just how fierce
OL,14,Fthe competition was. I've been trying
OL,15,Fto write for as long as I can remember
OL,16,Fand I'm committed to making work
OL,17,Fthat's interesting, has something to
OL,18,Fsay and is - even better - fun.
